posting_body: ['Cedar Green Apartments', '1145 116th Ave NE', 'Blaine, MN 55434', 'show contact info', 'Unit Information:', 'Studio Bedroom | 1 Bath', 'Unit Size:', '552 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent:', '$1345', 'Lease Terms:', 'Variable', 'Unit Includes:', '◾ Central Heating & Cooling', '◾ Dishwasher & Garbage Disposal', '◾ High Speed Internet: Cable & Century', 'OnLink Ready', '◾ Huge Covered Deck', '◾ Kitchen', '◾', 'Extra Large Walk-in Closets', '◾', 'In-home Washer & Dryer', '◾ Quartz Countertops', '◾ Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Property Description:', 'We are excited to offer a variety of studio, one and two bedroom apartment homes planned with your lifestyle in mind.', 'Each apartment is outfitted with the latest finishes, fixtures and sophisticated designs.', 'All units feature spacious floor plans and include stainless steel appliances, kitchen islands, quartz countertops and a full-size in-home washer and dryer.', 'Located right off 117th', 'Ave. NE and Central Ave.', 'NE, Cedar Green provides a comfy, cozy and convenient place to call home.', 'Property Amenities:', '◾ 5th Floor Sky View Community Room', '◾ Conference Room', '◾ Dog Park', '◾ Fitness Center', '◾ Game Room', '◾ Garden Plaza', '◾ Playground', '◾ Storage lockers Available', '◾ FOB Controlled Building Access', '◾ Heated, Underground Parking', '◾ Outdoor Fireplace, Fire Table & Courtyard', '◾ Outdoor Kitchen', '◾ Party Room', '◾ Pet Wash Station', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Call us today!', 'show contact info', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Pet Ownership Policy:', 'Pets - allowed Comments: We welcome your furry friends!', 'Maximum of 2 pets allowed.', 'Maximum weight of 40-60 lbs.', 'each *Breed Restrictions and Deposit Fees apply* Dog Fee & Deposit: $250 each due at time of move-in.', 'Cat Fee & Deposit: $350 each due at time of move-in.', 'Pet Rent: 45 per month only one cat allowed.', 'Proudly managed by Peak Living', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '25DFE95A81AE48F2']
